** The tube is pretty famous for making it easy to get about
** [[http://www.tfl.gov.uk/assets/downloads/standard-tube-map.pdf|the Tube Map (pdf)]]
** Buses are good too because you get to do some sightseeing on the way
** Get yourself an [[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oyster_card|Oyster Card]]. London public transport without one is very expensive.
** [[http://www.tfl.gov.uk/gettingaround/maps/buses/pdf/central-london-bus-map.pdf|central London Bus map (pdf)]]
** [[http://www.tfl.gov.uk/gettingaround/maps/buses/|Bus route page]]
